" or just looking to expand your climbing circle, this event is for you."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກໆສອງອາທິດ, ພວກເຮົາຈັດກິດຈະກຳປີນຜານັດເດດ: ເປັນຊ່ວງເວລາການປີນຜາທີ່ຜ່ອນຄາຍ ແລະ ເປັນກັນເອງ ເຊິ່"
"ງນັກປີນຜາສາມາດພົບເພື່ອນໃໝ່ໃນການຊ່ວຍດຶງເຊືອກ (Belay), ຄູ່ປີນຜາເຕ້ຍ ຫຼື ອາດຈະເປັນຄູ່ນັດເດດ. ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານ"
"ຈະເປັນສະມາຊິກໃໝ່, ເປັນຄົນໃໝ່ໃນເມືອງນີ້ ຫຼື ພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງການຂະຫຍາຍວົງການນັກປີນຜາຂອງທ່ານ, ກິດຈະກຳນີ້ແມ່"
"ນເໝາະສຳລັບທ່ານ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Find out signed documents from the smart button at the top of the contact "
"form labelled Signature Requested."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນຫາເອກະສານທີ່ລົງລາຍເຊັນແລ້ວໄດ້ຈາກປຸ່ມລັດຢູ່ທາງເທິງຂອງແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່ ທີ່ມີຊື່ວ່າ \"ຮ້ອງຂໍລາຍເຊັນແລ້ວ\"."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_1
msgid "Fresh, competition-grade boulders set by elite route setters"
msgstr ""
"ເສັ້ນທາງປີນຜາເຕ້ຍໃໝ່ໆ ລະດັບການແຂ່ງຂັນ ທີ່ອອກແບບໂດຍຜູ້ກຳນົດເສັ້ນທາງມືອາຊີບ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_3
msgid "Friendly, low-pressure atmosphere"
msgstr "ບັນຍາກາດເປັນກັນເອງ, ບໍ່ມີຄວາມກົດດັນ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Generate visibility through the <strong>Website App</strong>"
msgstr "ສ້າງການຮັບຮູ້ຜ່ານ <strong>ແອັບເວັບໄຊ (Website App)</strong>"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Give it a name, adjust its dates, and then save it."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຊື່, ປັບແຕ່ງວັນທີ ແລະ ຫຼັງຈາກນັ້ນກົດບັນທຶກ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:pos.category,name:climbing_gym.pos_category_2
msgid "Goods"
msgstr "ສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:res.partner.grade,name:climbing_gym.res_partner_grade_data_happy_hour
msgid "Happy Hour"
msgstr "ແຮບປີ້ອາວເວີ (Happy Hour)"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:product.pricelist,name:climbing_gym.product_pricelist_3
msgid "Happy Hour Member"
msgstr "ສະມາຊິກ Happy Hour"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:loyalty.program,portal_point_name:climbing_gym.loyalty_program_3
msgid "Happy Hour Sessions"
msgstr "ຮອບ Happy Hour"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:loyalty.program,name:climbing_gym.loyalty_program_3
msgid "Happy Hour Sessions - 10"
msgstr "ຮອບ Happy Hour - 10 ຄັ້ງ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hit a Planning cell to plan a shift."
msgstr "ກົດທີ່ຊ່ອງໃນຕາຕະລາງແຜນງານເພື່ອວາງແຜນກະລາເວລານຳວຽກ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Hit the Auto Plan button beside the Publish one.<br/>This assign the shifts "
"to employees based on their roles."
msgstr ""
"ກົດປຸ່ມ \"ວາງແຜນອັດຕະໂນມັດ\" (Auto Plan) ທີ່ຢູ່ຂ້າງປຸ່ມເຜີຍແຜ່.<br/>ລະບົບຈະມອບໝາຍກະລາເວລານຳວ"
"ຽກໃຫ້ພະນັກງານໂດຍອີງຕາມບົດບາດຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hit the Sent Waiver button to request the signature."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ \"ສົ່ງໃບສະລະສິດ\" (Sent Waiver) ເພື່ອຮ້ອງຂໍລາຍເຊັນ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Hit the Unpublished toggle in order to publish it to your website visitors."
msgstr ""
"ກົດປຸ່ມສະຫຼັບ \"ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ເຜີຍແຜ່\" ເພື່ອເຜີຍແຜ່ໃຫ້ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົມເວັບໄຊເຫັນ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Hit the Use Session. This creates a new quote to consume a session, which is"
" paid with a discount in case of a subscription and with a loyalty session "
"in the case of session bundles."
msgstr ""
"ກົດປຸ່ມ \"ໃຊ້ຮອບບໍລິການ\" (Use Session). ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ເພື່ອຕັດຮອບການໃຊ້ງານ, ເຊິ່ງຈ"
"ະຖືກຈ່າຍດ້ວຍສ່ວນຫຼຸດໃນກໍລະນີການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກ ຫຼື ດ້ວຍຄະແນນສະສົມໃນກໍລະນີແພັກເກດຮອບບໍລິການ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_3
msgid "Icebreaker games and climbing challenges"
msgstr "ກິດຈະກຳລະລາຍພຶດຕິກຳ ແລະ ການທ້າທາຍການປີນຜາ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.homepage
msgid "Ideal to discover climbing or when you pass by here!"
msgstr "ເໝາະສຳລັບການທົດລອງປີນຜາ ຫຼື ເວລາທີ່ທ່ານຜ່ານມາກາຍແຖວນີ້!"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next Knowledge Article)"
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນແນະນຳ, ທ່ານຄວນນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ (Demo data) ແລະ ທົດລອ"
"ງໃຊ້ Demo - Use Case (ໃນບົດຄວາມຄວາມຮູ້ຖັດໄປ)"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In this configuration, products are not tracked in terms of count but feel "
"free to explore<strong> Inventory App</strong> to setup the appropriate "
"products and benefit from capabilities which meet your needs."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້, ຈະບໍ່ມີການຕິດຕາມຈຳນວນສິນຄ້າ ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດສຳຫຼວດ <strong>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ "
"(Inventory App)</strong> ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າສິນຄ້າທີ່ເໝາະສົມ ແລະ ນຳໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ຕອບໂຈດຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອ"
"ງທ່ານ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_2
msgid "Instruction on outdoor safety, techniques, and etiquette"
msgstr "ຄຳແນະນຳກ່ຽວກັບຄວາມປອດໄພຂ້າງນອກ, ເຕັກນິກ ແລະ ມາລະຍາດ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:planning.role,name:climbing_gym.planning_role_2
msgid "Instructor"
msgstr "ຄູຝຶກ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:climbing_gym.x_is_base_entrance
msgid "Is Base Entrance"
msgstr "ແມ່ນການເຂົ້າໃຊ້ພື້ນຖານ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:climbing_gym.x_is_waiver
msgid "Is Waiver"
msgstr "ແມ່ນໃບສະລະສິດ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Join us for our Monthsly Outdoor Climbing Sessions, where we take the skills"
" from the gym and head out to real rock. These guided trips are designed to "
"help climbers of all levels experience the thrill of outdoor climbing in a "
"safe, supportive setting."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມກັບພວກເຮົາສຳລັບກິດຈະກຳປີນຜານອກສະຖານທີ່ປະຈຳເດືອນ, ບ່ອນທີ່ພວກເຮົາຈະນຳທັກສະຈາກໃນຢິມໄປໃຊ້ກັ"
"ບຜາແທ້ໆ. ທິບທີ່ມີຜູ້ນຳທ່ຽວນີ້ຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ນັກປີນຜາທຸກລະດັບໄດ້ສຳຜັດກັບຄວາມຕື່ນເຕັ້ນຂອງການປີນຜານ"
"ອກສະຖານທີ່ໃນສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ປອດໄພ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Leverage the shift templates for recurrent shifts by roles.<br/>You can edit"
" those from the Configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບກະລາເວລານຳວຽກສຳລັບວຽກທີ່ເຮັດຊ້ຳຕາມບົດບາດ.<br/>ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ຈາກເມນູກາ"
"ນຕັ້ງຄ່າ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Leverage the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> </font><font>Barcode "
"App</font></strong> to manipulate subscription and loyalty cards"
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> </font><font>ແອັບບາໂຄດ (Barcode "
"App)</font></strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການບັດສະມາຊິກ ແລະ ບັດສະສົມຄະແນນ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_3
msgid "Lightly structured partner rotations to keep things flowing"
msgstr "ການໝູນວຽນຄູ່ປີນຜາຢ່າງເປັນລະບົບເພື່ອໃຫ້ກິດຈະກຳດຳເນີນໄປຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:product.template,name:climbing_gym.product_template_21
msgid "Liquid Chalk"
msgstr "ຊອກຂາວແບບນ້ຳ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_1
msgid "Live DJ, MC, and food trucks on-site"
msgstr "ມີດີເຈສົດ, ພິທີກອນ ແລະ ລົດຂາຍອາຫານ (Food trucks) ພາຍໃນງານ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage waiver with the <strong>Sign App</strong>"
msgstr "ຈັດການໃບສະລະສິດດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບລົງລາຍເຊັນ (Sign App)</strong>"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage your employees' shifts with the <strong>Planning App</strong>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການກະລາເວລານຳວຽກຂອງພະນັກງານດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning App)</strong>"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:event.event,subtitle:climbing_gym.event_event_3
msgid "Meet your new climbing buddy"
msgstr "ພົບກັບເພື່ອນປີນຜາຄົນໃໝ່ຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Monitoring consumed entrances might be a good idea to capture rush hours..."
msgstr ""
"ການຕິດຕາມຈຳນວນການເຂົ້າໃຊ້ທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້ໄປ ເປັນວິທີທີ່ດີໃນການເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຊ່ວງເວລາທີ່ມີຄົນຫຼາຍ (Rush hours)..."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:event.tag,name:climbing_gym.event_tag_1
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "ລາຍເດືອນ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_2
msgid "Monthsly trips to top local climbing areas"
msgstr "ທິບປະຈຳເດືອນໄປຍັງພື້ນທີ່ປີນຜາຊື່ດັງໃນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"More advanced capabilities are available for you to create multi slot "
"events, paid event and more!"
msgstr ""
"ຄຸນສົມບັດຂັ້ນສູງມີໃຫ້ທ່ານໃຊ້ເພື່ອສ້າງງານກິດຈະກຳທີ່ມີຫຼາຍຊ່ວງເວລາ, ກິດຈະກຳທີ່ມີຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ!"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.contactus
msgid "My Company"
msgstr "ບໍລິສັດຂອງຂ້ອຍ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Navigate to the next week where no shifts are planned so far."
msgstr "ໄປທີ່ອາທິດຖັດໄປທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ທັນມີການວາງແຜນກະລາເວລານຳວຽກ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Next time you new customer comes at the desk to use an entrance, whether "
"from the subscription or the loyalty card, you will consume an entrance."
msgstr ""
