#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.homepage
msgid ""
"The perfect solution to transition to a more frequent "
"practice.<br/>Entrances are personal and related to your account."
msgstr ""
"ທາງເລືອກທີ່ສົມບູນແບບເພື່ອປ່ຽນມາຝຶກຊ້ອມໃຫ້ເລື້ອຍຂຶ້ນ.<br/>ການເຂົ້າໃຊ້ແມ່ນເປັນສິດສ່ວນບຸກຄົນ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"
"ກັບບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນລວມຢູ່ໃນການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ; ລອງສຳຫຼວດເບິ່ງໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.homepage
msgid ""
"The ultimate way to practice to the next level!<br/>Subscriptions are "
"personal and related to your account."
msgstr ""
"ວິທີທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດໃນການຝຶກຊ້ອມໄປສູ່ອີກລະດັບ!<br/>ການສະໝັກສະມາຊິກແມ່ນເປັນສິດສ່ວນບຸກຄົນ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບບັນຊີ"
"ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To handle the front desk, to provide lessons and more, employees are needed."
" And to organize all this, <strong>Planning App </strong>is the place to be."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຈັດການວຽກຕ້ອນຮັບ, ການສອນ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີພະນັກງານ. ແລະ ເພື່ອຈັດລະບຽບທັງໝົດນີ້, "
"<strong>ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning App)</strong> ແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ຕອບໂຈດ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To make some noise and generate a feeling of community among your customer, "
"you most likely are organizing events. The <strong>Events App </strong>got "
"your back for this."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອສ້າງກະແສ ແລະ ຄວາມຮູ້ສຶກຂອງການເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຊຸມຊົນໃນກຸ່ມລູກຄ້າ, ທ່ານອາດຈະມີການຈັດກິດຈະກຳຕ່າງ"
"ໆ. <strong>ແອັບກິດຈະກຳ (Events App)</strong> ຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານໃນເລື່ອງນີ້."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To manage waivers, we take advantage of the <strong>Sign App </strong>from "
"the customer form."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຈັດການໃບສະລະສິດ, ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ປະໂຫຍດຈາກ <strong>ແອັບລົງລາຍເຊັນ (Sign App)</strong> ຜ່"
"ານແບບຟອມລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:event.event,description:climbing_gym.event_event_2
msgid "Transportation from the climbing gym"
msgstr "ມີລົດຮັບສົ່ງຈາກໂຮງຍິມປີນຜາ"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid "Two types of product can be sold to access the climbing area:"
msgstr "ສິນຄ້າສອງປະເພດທີ່ສາມາດຂາຍເພື່ອເຂົ້າໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ປີນຜາໄດ້ຄື:"

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model:res.partner.grade,name:climbing_gym.res_partner_grade_data_unlimited
